description: Red Pine Exploration Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mining properties in Canada. Its flagship project is the Wawa Gold Project that covers an area of 6,800 hectares located to the east of the Town of Wawa in northern Ontario. The company was formerly known as Vencan Gold Corporation and changed its name to Red Pine Exploration Inc. in March 2009. Red Pine Exploration Inc. was incorporated in 1936 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
